<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir ew nehst
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> spiler <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, also sind
                        die spiler <add>sider</add> czü uns her heim kumen und wir
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit in <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        da von geredt und etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats dar czü
                                <expan>beschied<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz man frewntlich
                                <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> geredt hat, so
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>re</expan> daz das <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> berichtet <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        ist, also daz sie in bey leben <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        dem armen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>güt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> willen beweisen wöllet und
                                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pürggelts</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, also daz er unser
                            <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> geniesse. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
